Here is an example\nconfiguration that sets up a single MCP server, for GitHub:</p><div data-code=\"id#4\"><span><div class=\"monaco-tokenized-source\" style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0, &quot;calt&quot; 0; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 19px; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"mtk1\">{</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk10\">\"mcpServers\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: {</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk10\">\"github\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: {</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span><span class=\"mtk10\">\"command\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk12\">\"npx\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span><span class=\"mtk10\">\"args\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: [</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">        </span><span class=\"mtk12\">\"-y\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">        </span><span class=\"mtk12\">\"@modelcontextprotocol/server-github\"</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">      ],</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span><span class=\"mtk10\">\"env\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: {</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">        </span><span class=\"mtk10\">\"GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk12\">\"&lt;YOUR_TOKEN&gt;\"</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">      }</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">    }</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">  }</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></div></span></div><p>Remote MCP connections are also supported. Here is an example configuration for the remote GitHub MCP server:</p><div data-code=\"id#5\"><span><div class=\"monaco-tokenized-source\" style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0, &quot;calt&quot; 0; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 19px; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span class=\"mtk1\">{</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk10\">\"mcpServers\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: {</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk10\">\"remote-github\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: {</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span><span class=\"mtk10\">\"serverUrl\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk12\">\"https://api.githubcopilot.com/mcp/\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span><span class=\"mtk10\">\"headers\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: {</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">        </span><span class=\"mtk10\">\"Authorization\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk12\">\"Bearer &lt;YOUR_TOKEN&gt;\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">        </span><span class=\"mtk10\">\"Content-Type\"</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk12\">\"application/json\"</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">      }</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">    }</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">  }</span><br><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></div></span></div></div><div class=\"docs-sentence\">There is a growing ecosystem of MCP servers that you can find online. See the <span class=\"link\">docs</span> for more information.</div></div></div><div class=\"collapse-button\"><div class=\"antigravity-collapse-icon\" style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><svg preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" class=\"size-6\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 9V4.5M9 9H4.5M9 9 3.75 3.75M9 15v4.5M9 15H4.5M9 15l-5.25 5.25M15 9h4.5M15 9V4.5M15 9l5.25-5.25M15 15h4.5M15 15v4.5m0-4.5 5.25 5.25\"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class=\"antigravity-editor-info-widget collapsed\" widgetid=\"antigravity.rulesFileInfoWidget\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"position: absolute; display: none;\"><div class=\"contents\"><div class=\"antigravity-rules-file-info-widget\"><h2></h2><div class=\"content\"><span></span><div class=\"example-container\"><span>An example rules file might look like this:</span><pre class=\"example-config\">1. My build system is Bazel\n2. My testing framework is pytest\n3. Don't modify any files in ...\n4. Don't use these APIs ...</pre></div><span></span></div></div></div><div class=\"collapse-button\"><div class=\"codicon codicon-info\"></div></div></div><div class=\"antigravity-editor-info-widget\"
